		<subsection name="Matlab Component Runtime redistributables">

			<p>
				If you downloaded the packaged versions and intend to use signal analysis
				methods which use Matlab, you will have to have the Matlab Component
				Runtime (or Matlab itself) installed. 
			</p>
			
			<p>
				Lack of MCR doesn't affect remaining functionality and may be ignored if not
				needed.			
			</p>
			
